5:T4b8,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"SoftwareApplication","@id":"https://www.xrnotify.io/#app","name":"XRNotify","description":"Real-time webhook notification platform for the XRP Ledger.","url":"https://www.xrnotify.io","applicationCategory":"DeveloperApplication","operatingSystem":"Web","offers":[{"@type":"Offer","name":"Free","price":"0","priceCurrency":"USD","description":"1,000 events/month, 2 webhooks"},{"@type":"Offer","name":"Starter","price":"29.00","priceCurrency":"USD","description":"50,000 events/month, 10 webhooks, WebSocket access"},{"@type":"Offer","name":"Pro","price":"99.00","priceCurrency":"USD","description":"500,000 events/month, 50 webhooks, priority delivery"}],"creator":{"@id":"https://www.jonomor.com/ali-morgan#person"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://www.jonomor.com/#organization"},"isPartOf":{"@id":"https://www.jonomor.com/#organization"},"featureList":["Real-time XRPL event ingestion","HMAC-SHA256 signed webhook delivery","Automatic retries with exponential backoff","Dead-letter queue for failed deliveries","Event replay and reprocessing","23+ XRPL event types supported","Developer dashboard with delivery logs","Per-webhook filtering by event type and account"]}6:Tcff,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","@id":"https://www.xrnotify.io/#faqpage","name":"XRNotify FAQ — Common Questions About XRPL Webhooks","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"What is XRNotify?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"XRNotify is a real-time webhook notification platform for the XRP Ledger. It monitors XRPL transactions as they confirm on-chain, normalizes them into clean JSON schemas, and delivers them to your endpoints via HMAC-signed HTTPS POST requests. XRNotify eliminates the need to run your own XRPL node or build polling infrastructure."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What XRPL events does XRNotify support?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"XRNotify supports 23+ event types across all major XRPL transaction categories: payments (XRP and issued tokens), NFT operations (minting, burning, offers, transfers), DEX trades (OfferCreate, OfferCancel, AMM operations), trustline changes (TrustSet), escrow events (create, finish, cancel), check operations, and account-level changes like settings modifications and deletions."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How does webhook delivery work?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"When an XRPL transaction matches your configured filters, XRNotify normalizes the event, signs the payload with your webhook secret using HMAC-SHA256, and delivers it as an HTTPS POST to your endpoint. If delivery fails, XRNotify retries with exponential backoff (up to 10 attempts over 12 hours). Events that exhaust all retries are moved to a dead-letter queue for manual inspection and replay."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is XRNotify free?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"XRNotify offers a free tier with 1,000 events per month and 2 webhook endpoints — enough for testing and hobby projects. Paid plans start at $29/month (Starter: 50,000 events, 10 webhooks, WebSocket streaming) and $99/month (Pro: 500,000 events, 50 webhooks, priority delivery). Enterprise plans with custom SLAs are available on request."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How do I verify webhook signatures?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Every XRNotify webhook includes an X-XRNotify-Signature header containing an HMAC-SHA256 hash of the request body, computed using your webhook signing secret. To verify, compute the HMAC-SHA256 of the raw request body with your secret and compare it to the header value using a constant-time comparison function to prevent timing attacks."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Who built XRNotify?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"XRNotify was built by Ali Morgan, founder of Jonomor, a systems architecture studio focused on AI Visibility and real-time infrastructure intelligence. XRNotify is the XRPL instrumentation layer of the Jonomor ecosystem, which also includes Guard-Clause, MyPropOps, The Neutral Bridge, Evenfield, and H.U.N.I.E."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is XRNotify part of a larger ecosystem?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. XRNotify is part of the Jonomor ecosystem, a suite of interconnected software products built by Ali Morgan. Within the ecosystem, XRNotify serves as the real-time observation layer — detecting XRPL events at the point of origin before they flow through interpretation and operational layers in other Jonomor properties."}}]}0:["pQjrRFT3j-NbWRfetFzsE",[[["",{"children":["docs",{"children":["reference",{"children":["retry-policy",{"children":["__PAGE__",{}]}]}]}]},"$undefined","$undefined",true],["",{"children":["docs",{"children":["reference",{"children":["retry-policy",{"children":["__PAGE__",{},[["$L1",["$","div",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-[#0a0a0f] text-white antialiased","children":[["$","nav",null,{"className":"border-b border-zinc-800/50","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm","children":[["$","$L2",null,{"href":"/docs","className":"text-zinc-500 hover:text-zinc-300 no-underline","children":"Docs"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-zinc-600","children":"/"}],["$","$L2",null,{"href":"/docs#reference","className":"text-zinc-500 hover:text-zinc-300 no-underline","children":"Reference"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-zinc-600","children":"/"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-zinc-300","children":"Retry Policy"}]]}],["$","$L2",null,{"href":"/dashboard","className":"text-zinc-400 hover:text-white transition-colors text-sm no-underline","children":"Dashboard →"}]]}]}],["$","main",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-10","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-block text-xs font-medium text-emerald-400 bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 rounded px-2 py-0.5 mb-4","children":"Reference"}],["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-3","children":"Retry Policy"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-zinc-400 text-lg leading-relaxed","children":"XRNotify guarantees at-least-once delivery. If your endpoint does not return a 2xx status within 10 seconds, the delivery is retried automatically on an exponential backoff schedule."}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"mb-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4","children":"Overview"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-zinc-300 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3","children":"Every event detected on the XRPL is delivered to your webhook endpoint at least once. In practice, the vast majority of deliveries succeed on the first attempt. The retry mechanism exists to handle transient failures — network blips, brief endpoint unavailability, or accidental non-2xx responses."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-zinc-300 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":["Because retries are a normal part of the delivery guarantee, your webhook handler must be idempotent. Use the"," ",["$","code",null,{"className":"text-emerald-400 bg-zinc-800 px-1 rounded","children":"X-XRNotify-Delivery-Id"}]," header or the deterministic"," ",["$","code",null,{"className":"text-emerald-400 bg-zinc-800 px-1 rounded","children":"event_id"}]," field to detect and safely skip duplicate deliveries."]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"mb-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4","children":"Retry schedule"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"overflow-x-auto mb-4","children":["$","table",null,{"className":"w-full text-sm border-collapse","children":[["$","thead",null,{"children":["$","tr",null,{"className":"border-b border-zinc-800","children":[["$","th",null,{"className":"text-left py-2 pr-6 text-zinc-400 font-medium","children":"Attempt"}],["$","th",null,{"className":"text-left py-2 pr-6 text-zinc-400 font-medium","children":"Delay after previous"}],["$","th",null,{"className":"text-left py-2 pr-6 text-zinc-400 font-medium","children":"Cumulative elapsed"}],["$","th",null,{"className":"text-left py-2 text-zinc-400 font-medium","children":"Notes"}]]}]}],["$","tbody",null,{"className":"divide-y divide-zinc-800/50","children":[["$","tr","1",{"children":[["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 pr-6 text-zinc-300","children":"1"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 pr-6 text-zinc-300","children":"Immediate"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 pr-6 text-zinc-300","children":"0s"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 text-zinc-500 text-xs","children":"Initial delivery"}]]}],["$","tr","2",{"children":[["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 pr-6 text-zinc-300","children":"2"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 pr-6 text-zinc-300","children":"1 minute"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 pr-6 text-zinc-300","children":"~1m"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 text-zinc-500 text-xs","children":"First retry"}]]}],["$","tr","3",{"children":[["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 pr-6 text-zinc-300","children":"3"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 pr-6 text-zinc-300","children":"5 minutes"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 pr-6 text-zinc-300","children":"~6m"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 text-zinc-500 text-xs","children":""}]]}],["$","tr","4",{"children":[["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 pr-6 text-zinc-300","children":"4"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 pr-6 text-zinc-300","children":"30 minutes"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 pr-6 text-zinc-300","children":"~36m"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 text-zinc-500 text-xs","children":""}]]}],["$","tr","5",{"children":[["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 pr-6 text-zinc-300","children":"5"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 pr-6 text-zinc-300","children":"2 hours"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 pr-6 text-zinc-300","children":"~2.6h"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 text-zinc-500 text-xs","children":""}]]}],["$","tr","6",{"children":[["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 pr-6 text-zinc-300","children":"6"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 pr-6 text-zinc-300","children":"6 hours"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 pr-6 text-zinc-300","children":"~8.6h"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 text-zinc-500 text-xs","children":""}]]}],["$","tr","7",{"children":[["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 pr-6 text-zinc-300","children":"7"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 pr-6 text-zinc-300","children":"12 hours"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 pr-6 text-zinc-300","children":"~20.6h"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 text-zinc-500 text-xs","children":""}]]}],["$","tr","8",{"children":[["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 pr-6 text-zinc-300","children":"8"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 pr-6 text-zinc-300","children":"24 hours"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 pr-6 text-zinc-300","children":"~44.6h"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 text-zinc-500 text-xs","children":"Final attempt"}]]}]]}]]}]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":["After 8 failed attempts, the delivery moves to"," ",["$","code",null,{"className":"text-emerald-400 bg-zinc-800 px-1 rounded","children":"dead"}]," status. No further automatic retries occur. You can still trigger a manual retry at any time."]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"mb-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4","children":"What counts as a failure"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-zinc-300 text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed","children":"A delivery attempt is marked as failed if any of the following occur:"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"space-y-2 text-zinc-300 text-sm","children":[["$","li","HTTP status 3xx, 4xx, or 5xx returned by your endpoint",{"className":"flex gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-red-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5","children":"✕"}],["$","span",null,{"children":"HTTP status 3xx, 4xx, or 5xx returned by your endpoint"}]]}],["$","li","No response received within 10 seconds (connection timeout)",{"className":"flex gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-red-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5","children":"✕"}],["$","span",null,{"children":"No response received within 10 seconds (connection timeout)"}]]}],["$","li","SSL/TLS handshake failure or expired certificate",{"className":"flex gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-red-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5","children":"✕"}],["$","span",null,{"children":"SSL/TLS handshake failure or expired certificate"}]]}],["$","li","DNS resolution failure for your endpoint's hostname",{"className":"flex gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-red-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5","children":"✕"}],["$","span",null,{"children":"DNS resolution failure for your endpoint's hostname"}]]}],["$","li","Connection refused (e.g., server is down or port not open)",{"className":"flex gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-red-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5","children":"✕"}],["$","span",null,{"children":"Connection refused (e.g., server is down or port not open)"}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-2 text-zinc-300 text-sm","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"text-zinc-400 text-xs","children":["A delivery is considered ",["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-emerald-400","children":"successful"}]," if:"]}],[["$","div","HTTP status 200–299 returned within 10 seconds",{"className":"flex gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-emerald-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5","children":"✓"}],["$","span",null,{"children":"HTTP status 200–299 returned within 10 seconds"}]]}]]]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"mb-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4","children":"Jitter"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-zinc-300 text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed","children":"Each retry delay has ±10% random jitter applied. This prevents a thundering herd scenario where many deliveries that failed simultaneously all retry at exactly the same time, which could overwhelm your endpoint."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-4 overflow-x-auto mb-4","children":["$","pre",null,{"className":"text-zinc-300 text-sm font-mono whitespace-pre","children":"# Backoff formula with jitter:\ndelay(attempt) = base_delay[attempt] × (1 + random(-0.1, 0.1))\n\n# Example — attempt 3 base delay = 5 minutes:\n# Actual delay will be between 4m30s and 5m30s"}]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"mb-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4","children":"Auto-disable behavior"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-zinc-300 text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed","children":["Each webhook tracks a"," ",["$","code",null,{"className":"text-emerald-400 bg-zinc-800 px-1 rounded","children":"consecutive_failures"}]," counter. This counter increments each time a delivery reaches the final failed state (after all 8 attempts), and resets to zero on any successful delivery."]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-zinc-300 text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed","children":["If ",["$","code",null,{"className":"text-emerald-400 bg-zinc-800 px-1 rounded","children":"consecutive_failures"}]," reaches 100, XRNotify automatically sets the webhook status to ",["$","code",null,{"className":"text-emerald-400 bg-zinc-800 px-1 rounded","children":"disabled"}]," and sends an email notification to your account's registered email address."]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-amber-500/10 border border-amber-500/20 rounded-lg p-3 text-sm text-zinc-300 mb-4","children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-amber-300","children":"Auto-disable:"}]," A disabled webhook stops receiving new events. No events are queued during the disabled period — use the Replay API to recover missed events after re-enabling."]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-zinc-300 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"Re-enable a disabled webhook via the dashboard or the API:"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-4 overflow-x-auto mt-3","children":["$","pre",null,{"className":"text-zinc-300 text-sm font-mono whitespace-pre","children":"curl -X PATCH https://api.xrnotify.io/v1/webhooks/wh_abc123 \\\n  -H \"X-XRNotify-Key: xrn_live_xxx\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{ \"status\": \"active\" }'"}]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"mb-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4","children":"Delivery status values"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"overflow-x-auto","children":["$","table",null,{"className":"w-full text-sm border-collapse","children":[["$","thead",null,{"children":["$","tr",null,{"className":"border-b border-zinc-800","children":[["$","th",null,{"className":"text-left py-2 pr-6 text-zinc-400 font-medium","children":"Status"}],["$","th",null,{"className":"text-left py-2 text-zinc-400 font-medium","children":"Description"}]]}]}],["$","tbody",null,{"className":"divide-y divide-zinc-800/50","children":[["$","tr","pending",{"children":[["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 pr-6","children":["$","code",null,{"className":"text-emerald-400 text-xs","children":"pending"}]}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 text-zinc-300 text-xs leading-relaxed","children":"Queued for initial delivery or awaiting a scheduled retry."}]]}],["$","tr","delivering",{"children":[["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 pr-6","children":["$","code",null,{"className":"text-emerald-400 text-xs","children":"delivering"}]}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 text-zinc-300 text-xs leading-relaxed","children":"Currently being sent to your endpoint."}]]}],["$","tr","succeeded",{"children":[["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 pr-6","children":["$","code",null,{"className":"text-emerald-400 text-xs","children":"succeeded"}]}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 text-zinc-300 text-xs leading-relaxed","children":"Your endpoint returned a 2xx status within the timeout."}]]}],["$","tr","failed",{"children":[["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 pr-6","children":["$","code",null,{"className":"text-emerald-400 text-xs","children":"failed"}]}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 text-zinc-300 text-xs leading-relaxed","children":"All retry attempts have been exhausted. Manual action required."}]]}],["$","tr","dead",{"children":[["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 pr-6","children":["$","code",null,{"className":"text-emerald-400 text-xs","children":"dead"}]}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2.5 text-zinc-300 text-xs leading-relaxed","children":"Alias for failed — delivery will not be retried automatically."}]]}]]}]]}]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"mb-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4","children":"Manual retry"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-zinc-300 text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed","children":["Even after a delivery reaches ",["$","code",null,{"className":"text-emerald-400 bg-zinc-800 px-1 rounded","children":"failed"}]," status, you can trigger an immediate re-attempt:"]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-4 overflow-x-auto mb-4","children":["$","pre",null,{"className":"text-zinc-300 text-sm font-mono whitespace-pre","children":"curl -X POST https://api.xrnotify.io/v1/deliveries/dlv_abc123/retry \\\n  -H \"X-XRNotify-Key: xrn_live_xxx\""}]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":["The response includes the delivery object with the updated"," ",["$","code",null,{"className":"text-emerald-400 bg-zinc-800 px-1 rounded","children":"status"}],","," ",["$","code",null,{"className":"text-emerald-400 bg-zinc-800 px-1 rounded","children":"response_code"}],", and"," ",["$","code",null,{"className":"text-emerald-400 bg-zinc-800 px-1 rounded","children":"last_error"}]," fields after the attempt completes."]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"mb-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4","children":"Bulk recovery with Replay"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-zinc-300 text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed","children":"For large-scale recovery — such as when your endpoint was down for several hours and hundreds of deliveries failed — use the Replay API to re-deliver all events matching a time window in one request, rather than retrying them individually."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-4 overflow-x-auto mb-4","children":["$","pre",null,{"className":"text-zinc-300 text-sm font-mono whitespace-pre","children":"curl -X POST https://api.xrnotify.io/v1/replay \\\n  -H \"X-XRNotify-Key: xrn_live_xxx\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"webhook_id\": \"wh_abc123\",\n    \"filters\": {\n      \"since\": \"2024-01-15T00:00:00Z\",\n      \"until\": \"2024-01-15T12:00:00Z\"\n    }\n  }'"}]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":["The Replay API re-delivers events as new deliveries with fresh"," ",["$","code",null,{"className":"text-emerald-400 bg-zinc-800 px-1 rounded","children":"X-XRNotify-Delivery-Id"}]," values. Because the"," ",["$","code",null,{"className":"text-emerald-400 bg-zinc-800 px-1 rounded","children":"event_id"}]," in the body is deterministic and unchanged, you can use it as a stable idempotency key. See the"," ",["$","$L2",null,{"href":"/docs/api/replay","className":"text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300","children":"Replay API reference"}]," ","for the full filter options."]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"mb-10","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-amber-500/10 border border-amber-500/20 rounded-lg p-3 text-sm text-zinc-300 mb-4","children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-amber-300","children":"Idempotency is required."}]," Because XRNotify retries deliveries, your endpoint may receive the same event more than once. Always implement idempotency using the"," ",["$","code",null,{"className":"text-emerald-400","children":"X-XRNotify-Delivery-Id"}]," header or the"," ",["$","code",null,{"className":"text-emerald-400","children":"event_id"}]," body field to detect and safely skip duplicate processing."]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 rounded-lg p-3 text-sm text-zinc-300","children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-white","children":"Secret rotation note:"}]," Events are retried against your webhook's current configuration. If you rotate your webhook secret between the original delivery and a retry, the retry will be signed with the new secret — not the original one. Ensure your signature verification uses the current secret stored in your environment."]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4","children":"Next steps"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3","children":[["$","$L2","/docs/guides/handling-failures",{"href":"/docs/guides/handling-failures","className":"block bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-zinc-700 transition-colors no-underline","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"text-sm font-medium text-white mb-1","children":"Handling Failures Guide"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-xs text-zinc-500","children":"Practical patterns for resilient webhook handlers"}]]}],["$","$L2","/docs/api/replay",{"href":"/docs/api/replay","className":"block bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-zinc-700 transition-colors no-underline","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"text-sm font-medium text-white mb-1","children":"Replay API Reference"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-xs text-zinc-500","children":"Full spec for bulk event recovery"}]]}],["$","$L2","/docs/api/deliveries",{"href":"/docs/api/deliveries","className":"block bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-zinc-700 transition-colors no-u